              <zone forceUpdate='true' h='30618' id='11' type-v2='text' w='30659' x='357' y='19382'>
                <formatted-text>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>The Guaranteed Delivery variant generated a statistically significant </run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>28.5% relative lift in conversion</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>. However, it introduced a critical logistics bottleneck, driving SLA breach rates up to over </run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>30-40%</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> in rural and southern nodes. </run>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Recommendation:</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> Halt global rollout. Deploy variant exclusively in Warsaw/Poznań hubs to capture conversion lift without degrading customer trust in secondary regions.</run>
                </formatted-text>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
